data.description: Explore the ultimate blend of coziness and elegance in this lovely tri-level home. With four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and shiny hardwood floors, this roomy dwelling offers a perfect combination of space and style. The well-designed kitchen comes equipped with contemporary stainless steel appliances, making cooking easy and enjoyable. Enjoy sophisticated dinners in the formal dining area and experience the charm of connecting indoor and outdoor spaces with the walkout lower level. Relax and entertain on the back patio, surrounded by the expansive fenced backyard. Don't pass up the chance to turn this outstanding property into your permanent residence!
